        {
            "title": "OPEC+料將推進6月增產計劃 不受阿聯退出影響",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/t8H8YwWPBRcVaBSDkEjFBg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/indicatornews_1_M_1440048330.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com - 據路透社週六報導,引述知情人士消息,儘管阿拉伯聯合大公國意外退出,七個OPEC+成員國傾向於在6月將石油產量目標提高約188,000桶/日,聯盟將繼續推進增產計劃。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">報導稱,計劃中的增產幅度與上月20.6萬桶/日的增幅大致相當,經過調整以反映阿聯本週意外宣布將於5月1日退出該組織後的份額變化。這一決定顯示其餘成員國採取照常運作的態度。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這七個國家定於週日舉行線上會議。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">阿聯是OPEC第四大產油國,週二宣布在成為成員國近60年後退出該組織,使阿布達比擺脫了該組織用於平衡全球供需的產量目標限制。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-bce3c99e-61f7-36e2-8171-914103cd9613-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">路透社上週報導,這一退出令市場感到震驚。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">代表們上週表示,此次退出將削弱該產油國組織對全球石油市場的控制力,但預計其餘成員國將繼續團結在一起,並繼續協調供應政策。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">在與美國-以色列對伊朗戰爭相關的產量削減之前,阿布達比的日產量約為340萬桶——約佔全球原油供應的3%——使其成為有史以來退出該組織的最大產油國。</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/opec-%E6%96%99%E5%B0%87%E6%8E%A8%E9%80%B26%E6%9C%88%E5%A2%9E%E7%94%A2%E8%A8%88%E5%8A%83-%E4%B8%8D%E5%8F%97%E9%98%BF%E8%81%AF%E9%80%80%E5%87%BA%E5%BD%B1%E9%9F%BF-120012088.html",
